  'lunch-picker': ['A lunch picker selects one item from the available menu list. Every remaining option has the same chance when the picker uses uniform random selection.', 'Choose a preset or enter one lunch option per line, remove anything unavailable, and spin. Avoiding recent winners can add variety across several meals.', 'The result is a suggestion, not a dietary recommendation. Check allergies, ingredients, nutrition needs, opening hours, price, and availability before ordering.'],
  'color-converter': ['HEX, RGB, RGBA, and HSL are different notations for describing colors. Converting the notation should preserve the represented color while exposing components suited to a particular design or code workflow.', '#3f3f46 represents RGB(63, 63, 70). An alpha value can then be added when transparency is required.', 'Display profiles, browser color management, transparency over different backgrounds, gamut limits, and Tailwind configuration can affect the final appearance or available token name.'],
